HEADWORD: grapefruit
<hw>grape"fruit`</hw> <pr>(gr⟦amac⟧p"fr⟦oomac⟧t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A citrus tree (<spn>Citrus paradisi</spn>) bearing
